EndEvent
Event &Acoes.Click
/* Generated by DVelop Work With Plus Pattern [Start] - Do not change */
Do Case Case &Acoes = 1 Do 'Do LancarQuantidades' Case &Acoes = 2 Do 'Do FinalizarOrdem' Case &Acoes = 3 Do 'Do EmitirNota' Case &Acoes = 4 Do 'Do Imprimir' Case &Acoes = 5 Do 'Do CancelarOrdem' EndCase &Acoes = 0
/* Generated by DVelop Work With Plus Pattern [End] - Do not change */
EndEvent
